<HEAD>Shultz To Try Peace Plan Again</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: Inserts new 10th graf, ``Deputy Secretary,'' with Whitehead
quote</NOTE>
<BYLINE>By BARRY SCHWEID</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>AP Diplomatic Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
