he first time. He visited <LOCATION> Peru </LOCATION> in 1985. <PERSON> John </PERSON> <PERSON> Paul </PERSON> is scheduled to spend his 68th birthday in <LOCATION> Paraguay </LOCATION> on May 18 and returns to <LOCATION> Rome </LOCATION> on May 19.
